section.p:
To display the link, you just need to set your SVG file as the content of one of the page
				margin
				boxes:@page {
  @top-left {
    content: url("custom.svg");
  }
}

It is also possible to add a link inside the document header (or footer) by using the
					-oxy-link property on the @page margin box declaration.
				The entire page margin box will behave as a link and will be
				clickable.@page {
  @top-left {
    content: "Link";
    -oxy-link: "https://www.oxygenxml.com/";
    color:blue;
  } 
}
